{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw a bunch of block buildings, you know, like brick buildings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was Auschwitz One, the main camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, uh, I saw some characters that were-- that looked extremely healthy, very muscular, in, uh, in-- in uniforms of, uh-- at that time, I didn't know what uniform it was, but it wasn't a prison uniform.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There weren't too many, because they killed all the Russian soldiers and kept the minimum down there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I guess if the Red Cross came in, they want to show them that they still had some Russian prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some other Polish speaking or Ukrainian speaking guys that pushed a cart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Uh, the cart must have been about, [SIGHS] I don't know, eight, nine meters long, with very, very huge, four huge wheels.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, uh, in the front, there weren't horses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were people that are steering [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they stopped there in front of a block, and all of a sudden, bodies came shooting out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Later on, I learned that they were called the harvester commando, [GERMAN] kommando.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were the people that picked up the bodies that either were killed during the night or died during the night, and were laying down there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they picked them up, and then they put them to an assembly place, where they, later on, they're picked up on a truck and brought to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- I-- I-- I-- I did not recall this at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This would be an untruth, but when I came out, you know that-- there was a turmoil in me when I came out because you're free.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What does freedom mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what it means.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
